c: 2
v: 109
t: "Abaningi abantu bencwadi bafisa sengathi banganiphindisela emumva ekungakholweni, emva kokuba senikholiwe ngenxa yomona wabo, emuva kweqiniso selibonakalisiwe lacaca kubona, ngakho-ke thethelelani ninganaki kuze kufike umyalelo kaMvelinqangi, ngempela uMvelinqangi unamandla ngaphezu kwakho konke"